    bodyHtml: "<p>OrgTP uses Google sign-in (and email/password). Go to <strong>orgtp.com</strong>, click <strong>Sign In</strong>, and choose <strong>Continue with Google</strong> or enter your email and password.</p>\n<ul><li>If someone invited you, click the link in your invite email first — it ties your login to your seat in their organization.</li><li>Your login identity (email, password, two-factor) is managed on the <strong>Account</strong> settings page later (see §13).</li></ul>",
